creator: SK ID Solutions AS
descriptionHtml:
Smart-ID is the easiest, most convenient and safest way to authenticate yourself online ¬check your online bank account, access e-services and confirm transactions.

Smart-ID allows you to give signatures equal to handwritten signatures. This applies to all new Smart-IDs (except Basic level) issued since 08.11.2018.

Smart-ID is currently available for:
- Baltic states residents
- Estonian e-residents


EASY
Get started by downloading Smart-ID app.

Follow the steps in the app to confirm your identity and complete the registration process. Once you’ve done that, you’re good to go – no other confirmation needed!

CONVENIENT
Your Smart-ID is always within an easy reach!

You can use Smart-ID in as many smart devices as you want and gain access to your online accounts across all of them any time, any place. Using Smart-ID is free and totally unlimited.

SAFE

Smart-ID app does not store your identity or PIN codes. The app is used for key management: it creates your private keys while account registration and later mediates authentication and signature requests. User identity is managed securely by the service provider. A technology has been used in this product for which Cybernetica AS has filed a patent application or a patent has been granted.

Try out Smart-ID, visit portal.smart-id.com!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• For better convenience and clarity, users will be notified when their account usage is limited.
• For better security, we added a link to the support article on how to change PIN codes.
• Fixed WebView crash on some Android phones
• Improved the phone number validation process
• Improved situation where during registering SMS from an e-service provider arrived late and resulting error message
• Improved registering new Smart-ID with and existing Smart-ID so that less dialogues are used.
